{"tid":343981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(南海版盧溝橋事變)美國海軍在南海執行任務時失蹤","createTime":"2017-08-02T02:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T10:59:43.000Z","uid":63669,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84a9bdc9f49f82d9bc9c92ea5073cf1fc0881da8","tid":343981,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.phpi=20170802&amp;amp;s=10793096&amp;amp;a=57030842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.phpi%3D20170802%26amp%3Bs%3D10793096%26amp%3Ba%3D57030842&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=111c9527\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.phpi%3D20170802%26amp%3Bs%3D10793096%26amp%3Ba%3D57030842&h=462c0652\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.phpi=20170802&amp;amp;s=10793096&amp;amp;a=57030842</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/txq9o3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Ftxq9o3.jpg&h=e5613294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司報道稱，美國導彈驅逐艦「斯特西姆號」（USS Stethem），昨晨在南海執行例行任務期間，有一名海軍士兵失蹤。美國和日本船艦和飛機正在搜尋這名失蹤士兵，但美國官方沒有公佈這名水兵的姓名。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，「斯特西姆號」號軍艦上的士兵曾在艦上進行多次搜索，試圖找到失蹤水兵。美國海軍說，夏威夷人員救援聯合中心也在協助搜尋工作。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，美國官員在上月2日指，斯特西姆號曾駛入中國南海西沙群島的中建島12海浬範圍內。中國外交部事時後予以譴責，並強烈敦促美方立即停止此類嚴重侵犯中國主權、威脅中國安全的挑釁行動。"},{"pid":"6a89ad8ae954101d5c6cf8c8e9196b869c615449","tid":343981,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80bd05698183b8041fc876449e2d63ab2e9c029d","tid":343981,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:50:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ffcf789dba82abff39727bb95914c77152e6335","tid":343981,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"Viutv有要威又要戴頭盔，個海員話行船會有人比人扔落海"},{"pid